<paragraph blockId="227.[177,1387,721,1306]" box="[177,1089,957,991]" pageId="227" pageNumber="832">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[177,412,957,991]" pageId="227" pageNumber="832">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Car Nicobar Rat is nocturnal and arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
